#. <section class="sutta" id="sn48.9"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn48.9:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.9:0.2"
msgid "1. Suddhikavagga"
msgstr "1. Plain Version"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn48.9:0.3"
msgid "9. Paṭhamavibhaṅgasutta"
msgstr "9. Analysis (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.197"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.9:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, indriyāni."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five faculties."

msgctxt "sn48.9:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "sn48.9:1.3"
msgid "Saddhindriyaṃ … pe … paññindriyaṃ."
msgstr "The faculties of faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom."

msgctxt "sn48.9:1.4"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, saddhindriyaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the faculty of faith?"

msgctxt "sn48.9:1.5"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako saddho hoti, saddahati tathāgatassa bodhiṃ:"
msgstr "It’s when a noble disciple has faith in the Realized One’s awakening:"

msgctxt "sn48.9:1.6"
msgid ""
"‘itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū "
"anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’ti—"
msgstr ""
"‘That Blessed One is perfected, a fully awakened Buddha, accomplished in "
"knowledge and conduct, holy, knower of the world, supreme guide for those "
"who wish to train, teacher of gods and humans, awakened, blessed.’"

msgctxt "sn48.9:1.7"
msgid "idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, saddhindriyaṃ."
msgstr "This is called the faculty of faith."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.9:2.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, vīriyindriyaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the faculty of energy?"

msgctxt "sn48.9:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako āraddhavīriyo viharati akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"pahānāya, kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ upasampadāya, thāmavā daḷhaparakkamo "
"anikkhittadhuro kusalesu dhammesu—"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant lives with energy roused up for giving up unskillful "
"qualities and gaining skillful qualities. They’re strong, staunchly "
"vigorous, not slacking off when it comes to developing skillful qualities."

msgctxt "sn48.9:2.3"
msgid "idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, vīriyindriyaṃ."
msgstr "This is called the faculty of energy."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.9:3.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, satindriyaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the faculty of mindfulness?"

msgctxt "sn48.9:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako satimā hoti paramena satinepakkena samannāgato "
"cirakatampi cirabhāsitampi saritā anussaritā—"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a noble disciple is mindful. They have utmost mindfulness and "
"alertness, and can remember and recall what was said and done long ago."

msgctxt "sn48.9:3.3"
msgid "idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, satindriyaṃ."
msgstr "This is called the faculty of mindfulness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.9:4.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, samādhindriyaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the faculty of immersion?"

msgctxt "sn48.9:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako vossaggārammaṇaṃ karitvā labhati samādhiṃ, "
"labhati cittassa ekaggataṃ—"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a noble disciple, relying on letting go, gains immersion, gains "
"unification of mind."

msgctxt "sn48.9:4.3"
msgid "idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, samādhindriyaṃ."
msgstr "This is called the faculty of immersion."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.9:5.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, paññindriyaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the faculty of wisdom?"

msgctxt "sn48.9:5.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako paññavā hoti udayatthagāminiyā paññāya "
"samannāgato ariyāya nibbedhikāya, sammā dukkhakkhayagāminiyā—"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a noble disciple is wise. They have the wisdom of arising and "
"passing away which is noble, penetrative, and leads to the complete ending "
"of suffering."

msgctxt "sn48.9:5.3"
msgid "idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, paññindriyaṃ."
msgstr "This is called the faculty of wisdom."

msgctxt "sn48.9:5.4"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañcindriyānī”ti."
msgstr "These are the five faculties.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.9:5.5"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
